        "generateUrl": "https://developers.amadeus.com/my-apps",
        "setup": "First obtain an Amadeus `API Key` and `API Secret` from [My Self-Service Workspace](https://developers.amadeus.com/my-apps). Then request a bearer token with the OAuth2 client-credentials flow by `POST`ing form-encoded data to `https://test.api.amadeus.com/v1/security/oauth2/token` (or use `https://api.amadeus.com/v1/security/oauth2/token` with production keys) as documented in [Authorization](https://developers.amadeus.com/self-service/apis-docs/guides/developer-guides/API-Keys/authorization/). Send `grant_type=client_credentials`, `client_id`, and `client_secret`; the response returns `access_token` with `token_type` `Bearer`.",
        "acquisition": "manual"
      }
